00:05:35.710 --> 00:05:38.295
- Hey, goodness. -  Why are you sorting things out?

00:05:38.296 --> 00:05:41.423
-  Hey, what's gotten into you? - Why are you sorting them?

00:05:41.424 --> 00:05:43.425
