00:08:29.592 --> 00:08:32.636
But still, she completed chemo successfully multiple times,

00:08:32.637 --> 00:08:34.513
And she's gotten a lot better lately.

00:08:34.514 --> 00:08:35.724
Besides

00:08:36.558 --> 00:08:38.351
Besides

00:08:44.691 --> 00:08:49.487
There's no way the world would rob me of my grandma like that, right?

00:09:01.458 --> 00:09:02.709
You

00:09:06.588 --> 00:09:10.008
