00:19:34.799 --> 00:19:36.926
Yes, that's true.

00:19:38.177 --> 00:19:39.511
You have a point.

00:19:39.512 --> 00:19:42.515
Mmm. Eating together would only tire us out more.

00:19:43.015 --> 00:19:44.975
Then let's call it a day and not overdo it.

00:19:45.559 --> 00:19:48.187
I'll get going since I have some business to attend to.

