00:21:33.751 --> 00:21:37.462
Who knows? She might miraculously have a change of heart, no?

00:21:47.807 --> 00:21:50.517
Oh, goodness

00:21:50.518 --> 00:21:51.644
Ma'am, are you okay?

00:21:52.269 --> 00:21:53.270
What?

00:21:53.854 --> 00:21:54.980
Oh, my

00:21:55.481 --> 00:21:57.899
Dr. Do, what are you

00:21:57.900 --> 00:21:59.109
Let me help you with that.

00:22:00.110 --> 00:22:03.154
- Oh, be careful. - Right. Let me take that.

00:22:03.155 --> 00:22:05.491
- Goodness, thank you. - Take it slow.

00:22:08.536 --> 00:22:10.162
- Oh, man - Goodness.

00:22:19.922 --> 00:22:23.634
Hari's birthday is coming up in two days,

00:22:24.510 --> 00:22:27.011
So I was looking for a plate

00:22:27.012 --> 00:22:30.139
For red bean sorghum rice cakes

00:22:30.140 --> 00:22:32.935
But I have no strength in my wrists.

00:22:47.741 --> 00:22:49.326
Oh, man

00:22:52.872 --> 00:22:54.998
It's exhausting, isn't it?

00:22:54.999 --> 00:22:56.375
Not at all, ma'am.

00:23:01.213 --> 00:23:04.216
I've always made Hari

00:23:04.800 --> 00:23:07.261
These rice cakes

00:23:08.387 --> 00:23:10.681
On her birthdays.

00:23:11.307 --> 00:23:12.391
Oh

00:23:13.183 --> 00:23:16.603
Others only make them until their children turn ten,

00:23:16.604 --> 00:23:18.981
But I just kept on making them for her,

00:23:19.899 --> 00:23:25.404
So they may ward off misfortune and only bring good fortune Hari's way.

00:23:27.197 --> 00:23:30.867
