00:23:30.868 --> 00:23:33.537
When she lost her parents at the age of eight.

00:23:35.122 --> 00:23:37.249
So this was my way of wishing her the best

00:23:38.542 --> 00:23:41.920
In the days to come, with no more heartbreak.

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:47.551
But

00:23:48.344 --> 00:23:52.640
Hari's heart has been broken again,

00:23:53.849 --> 00:23:55.726
All because of me.

00:24:10.282 --> 00:24:13.911
Dr. Do Jiui

00:24:16.914 --> 00:24:21.251
PH docs leave after a year, right?

00:24:23.379 --> 00:24:24.463
Yes, ma'am.

00:24:30.386 --> 00:24:32.930
Regardless

00:24:35.557 --> 00:24:40.688
Can you stay by Hari's side for just a little while longer?

00:24:42.314 --> 00:24:47.361
Once I'm gone, she will be all alone

00:24:48.112 --> 00:24:50.655
And now that my time draws near,

00:24:50.656 --> 00:24:53.367
I can't help but worry about all sorts of things.

00:24:58.122 --> 00:24:59.415
Don't you worry, ma'am.

00:25:00.124 --> 00:25:01.625
I'll stay by Ms. Hari's side.

00:25:02.835 --> 00:25:05.461
I'll stay by her side even if she tells me to leave.

00:25:06.964 --> 00:25:08.590
Thank you.

00:25:17.349 --> 00:25:18.392
Why aren't you

00:25:19.935 --> 00:25:21.854
Letting her have her way this time?

00:25:27.651 --> 00:25:31.155
It's because I'm so scared.

00:25:39.288 --> 00:25:43.834
