How scared you must've been, all alone.

01:00:52.816 --> 01:00:55.068
But I'll hear you out now.

01:01:01.074 --> 01:01:05.120
Let me be scared with you, okay?

01:01:10.458 --> 01:01:11.710
Grandma, are you asleep?

01:01:14.838 --> 01:01:16.089
Grandma.

01:01:20.135 --> 01:01:22.220
Grandma, are you crying? Hmm?

01:01:32.355 --> 01:01:33.356
Grandma.

01:01:35.483 --> 01:01:36.693
Grandma.

01:01:37.777 --> 01:01:40.863
Grandma! Grandma, open your eyes.

01:01:40.864 --> 01:01:43.949
Grandma! No.

01:01:43.950 --> 01:01:46.619
You can't die! Grandma! Grandma!

01:01:46.620 --> 01:01:49.455
Grandma! Wake up!

01:01:49.456 --> 01:01:51.290
Grandma! Oh, no!

01:01:51.291 --> 01:01:53.043
PUBLIC HEALTH CENTER CLOSED

01:02:05.430 --> 01:02:07.890
Grandma, please

01:02:07.891 --> 01:02:10.184
Ms. Yuk, let me take a look at her.

01:02:12.812 --> 01:02:15.106
Save her.

01:02:15.607 --> 01:02:19.277
Please save my grandma. Please help.

01:02:20.737 --> 01:02:24.783
Please help save my grandma.

01:02:26.117 --> 01:02:28.161
Help her.

01:02:28.995 --> 01:02:31.581
No

01:02:37.420 --> 01:02:38.797
Ms. Oh Mija

01:02:42.050 --> 01:02:43.385
Has passed away

01:02:48.264 --> 01:02:49.766
At 19:34.

01:02:52.519 --> 01:02:55.980
No. No. No.

01:02:55.981 --> 01:02:59.067
No!

01:03:00.735 --> 01:03:02.654
No

01:03:06.908 --> 01:03:10.703
You never told me what you wanted to say!

01:03:10.704 --> 01:03:16.083
No, Grandma! Grandma!

01:03:16.084 --> 01:03:19.962
I didn't get to hear what you had to say.

01:03:19.963 --> 01:03:24.341
Grandma, you have to tell me.

01:03:24.342 --> 01:03:27.386
I didn't get to hear what you had to say.

01:03:27.387 --> 01:03:31.808
Wake up, Grandma! Grandma!

01:03:32.976 --> 01:03:34.518
No! No!

01:03:34.519 --> 01:03:37.104
- Wake up! - Ms. Yuk.

01:03:37.105 --> 01:03:40.233
Let go of me!

01:03:42.318 --> 01:03:47.448
Grandma. Grandma.

01:03:47.449 --> 01:03:52.494
I'm sorry, Grandma. I'm sorry.

01:03:52.495 --> 01:03:54.413
Wake up.

01:03:54.414 --> 01:03:57.207
I didn't get to hear what you had to say.

01:03:57.208 --> 01:03:59.543
I didn't get to hear

01:03:59.544 --> 01:04:05.424
Grandma, I'm sorry. Wake up!

01:04:05.425 --> 01:04:09.178
Grandma!

01:04:09.179 --> 01:04:13.183
Grandma.

01:04:28.406 --> 01:04:29.783
Grandma

01:04:33.203 --> 01:04:35.205
Grandma

01:04:50.637 --> 01:04:53.305
YOU'RE A DOCTOR WHO EVEN SUTURES UP THE WOUNDS

01:04:53.306 --> 01:04:56.684
OF A PATIENT WHO'S ALREADY PASSED AWAY

01:04:57.560 --> 01:04:59.978
SO,

01:04:59.979 --> 01:05:04.192
WHY WON'T YOU TEND TO MY HEART?

01:05:05.193 --> 01:05:08.613
THIS WAS HARI AND CHIYEON'S FIRST SHOOT

01:05:17.247 --> 01:05:20.625
LOVE IS A RIDE WITH NO BRAKES

01:05:21.209 --> 01:05:24.629
WHERE THE PASSION IS HIGHEST, THE DIRECTOR IS ALWAYS THERE

01:05:28.716 --> 01:05:31.636
DOCTOR ON THE EDGE

01:05:32.387 --> 01:05:35.097
Are you going to stop hanging out with that doctor?

01:05:35.098 --> 01:05:36.474
Please just pretend you don't see me.

01:05:38.017 --> 01:05:40.186
If he likes her so much, why did he do that?

01:05:40.770 --> 01:05:42.980
You should be sticking to her if you like her.

01:05:42.981 --> 01:05:44.566
That's what it means to like someone!

01:05:46.401 --> 01:05:48.361
I can't help it, even if it makes you hate me.

01:05:49.320 --> 01:05:51.071
One of the villagers has gone missing.

01:05:52.782 --> 01:05:54.867
Stay out of this. I said, stay out of it!

01:05:54.868 --> 01:05:56.785
What's the matter with you?

01:05:56.786 --> 01:05:58.830
Wouldn't anyone agree that I'm the better option?

01:06:01.875 --> 01:06:03.877
Translated by Yoon Hyuk Park

